      "text": "This was the state, like Michigan state, OK, like we are in Detroit, Michigan.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There was [INAUDIBLE], so all the whole [INAUDIBLE]-- villages, smaller town, all the surrounding towns, arrived to [INAUDIBLE].",
