    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they had to take I think about four or five more streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, of course, comes the law that you're not allowed to go from this surrounding.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Your area was like 10, 15-- I think it was about 15 blocks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we were very cramped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hundreds and hundreds of Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
